videos.headline: Santacaterina to Tears puts Northern Illinois on the board
videos.description: Daniel Santacaterina hits Spencer Tears on a 39-yard touchdown pass in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Mitch Kimble picked off by Mycial Allen
videos.description: Mycial Allen picks off Mitch Kimble and returns it 17-yards to set up Northern Illinois

videos.headline: Marcus Jones muscles ahead to extend Northern Illinois' lead
videos.description: Marcus Jones's 4-yard plunge extends the lead for the Huskies.

videos.headline: Mykelti Williams intercepts pass off deflection
videos.description: Mykelti Williams 10-yard interception return sets it up for the Huskies.

videos.headline: Marcus Jones plunges for a TD to extend the lead
videos.description: Marcus Jones one-yard touchdown run pushes the lead for the Huskies.

videos.headline: Joe Caputo intercepts pass off of tip drill
videos.description: Joe Caputo 14-yard interception stops the drive for Eastern Illinois.

videos.headline: Wimann scores to extend the lead
videos.description: Daniel Santacaterina's third TD pass pushes Northern Illinois lead to 35.

videos.headline: Gilkey Jr scores on the first TD for Eastern Illinois.
videos.description: Scotty Gilkey Jr scores on the QB sneak for the only TD for the Panthers.
